reviewText: Again, another garbled presentation from Harl.  He talks like he has pebbles in his mouth.  Hardly never leaves the podium, and when he does, the walks a few feet, and back he goes.  No eye contact with the audience/camera.  Very boring.
Lots to learn from these video's!
Awesome.. Any course you can get from Dr Kenneth Harl is well worth the time.  He is the best History Teacher !

Everyone of Prof. Harl's lecture series I have heard is first rate -- this one is no exception. As a retired lecturer myself I can only wish I had his ability on the podium -- his grasp of the material and his style (including some sly humor) are excellent
